as a matter of utmost urgency to take the necessary measures to 
protect the palestinians in the occupied territories 
to attribute the immediate cause for todays violent incidents 
to a socalled deranged person is a cynical and arrogant contempt 
of the facts he added 
israeli police who arrested the gunman said he was distraught 
over personal problems including a recent breakup with his 
girlfriend his identity was not released pending a court hearing 
 
